evelopment. You Will Assist in research and development of various product initiatives, including the CertiK Chain roadmap Coordinate Go-To-Market activities for the products, from coordinating launch dates to aligning training and announcement dates Develop product briefs, trainings, and other support materials for cross-functional team alignment Perform market research to establish strategic and high leverage product hypotheses Conduct user interviews for validation and iteration of product ideas You Have 1.5+ years of B2B SaaS product management experience Deep understanding of technical knowledge, such as software development process, databases, blockchain Ability to synthesize complex technical details to the relevant highlights Exceptional communication skills, both verbally and written Exceptional organizational skills and the ability to balance multiple things at a time (Preferred) Prior experience in blockchain, cybersecurity, or other technical field (Preferred) Prior experience in a fast-paced, growing start-up environment (Preferred) Prior UI/UX experience and basic design abilities ", 
